{"tid":2230373,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國安警拘網媒創辦人「涉去年傷人」變相追溯  許智峯斥濫權「所有罪都拉埋講」","createTime":"2020-10-05T01:14:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-05T01:16:30.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9582372d6f9a9937eefd01afc746b853734b2414","tid":2230373,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:14:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/TRQAXMMUJNFYZEFOUR4J65KUTE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FTRQAXMMUJNFYZEFOUR4J65KUTE%2F&d=A6Q0GQr%2FGmLii1x5qL7rGBSC%2F35X4DTIU%2BW3we%2FDSDs%3D&h=355c6fe9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201005%2FTRQAXMMUJNFYZEFOUR4J65KUTE%2F&h=bcdbce92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201005/TRQAXMMUJNFYZEFOUR4J65KUTE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n國安警拘網媒創辦人「涉去年傷人」變相追溯 <br />\n許智峯斥濫權「所有罪都拉埋講」<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方國安處成立後頻頻出動，多名政治人物被捕。其中曾代表民主派參選立法會飲食界的網媒「PPPN international」創辦人伍永德10月1日被國安處人員以「串謀有意圖傷人」罪名拘捕，但涉及案件是去年12月發生，即國安法生效前。立法會議員質疑警方藉此打壓異己，製造寒蟬效應。<br />\n<br />\n網媒「PPPN international」日前在facebook專頁公佈，創辦人伍永德早前被捕，律師指罪名為「串謀傷人」，他其後獲釋候查。本報曾向「PPPN international」及伍查詢詳情，昨晚未獲回覆。北京喉舌《文匯報》昨日引述消息指，伍懷疑涉與「屠龍小隊」案件有關。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9BkWIVI1quJDaLuI1va9AJiJza0=/1770x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/JMX3JWPA2JC4BB5W6Y53PRQ6YI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9BkWIVI1quJDaLuI1va9AJiJza0%3D%2F1770x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJMX3JWPA2JC4BB5W6Y53PRQ6YI.jpg&h=32d0f4ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■曾代表民主派參選的伍永德日前被捕。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n獲准保釋候查<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆指，國安處人員經深入調查後，10月1日在灣仔區拘捕一名34歲姓伍本地男子，涉嫌與一宗去年12月發生的「串謀有意圖傷人」案有關。該名被捕男子已獲准保釋候查，須於11月上旬向警方報到。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨立法會議員許智峯認為，警方此舉變相證明國安法有追溯力，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n許智峯續說，國安處較少針對普通市民，主要涉從政人物，如香。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察成員沈偉男表示，國安法不設追溯期，若國安處人員拘捕人。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n沈偉男又說，「串謀有意圖傷人」罪未必與國安法有關，若警方出動國安處調查，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n截至昨日，共28人涉嫌違反危害國家安全的行為和活動被警方拘捕，罪名包括分。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D04gRQ1uzuRSYsVbWnW64uHZG1k=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/YONGK7PGSFABBMPU5D4ILBXIRI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD04gRQ1uzuRSYsVbWnW64uHZG1k%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FYONGK7PGSFABBMPU5D4ILBXIRI.jpg&h=389cf368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■左報指伍永德疑與「屠龍小隊」案有關；圖為警方去年12月拘捕被指是屠龍小隊成員時引發警民衝突。"},{"pid":"63232cd98d6b20a7fbbb7da331cf40dfe2215955","tid":2230373,"uid":8681,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:16:30.000Z","msg":"根本成個香港政府都可以視為共產黨，邊有得分，中共滲透力勁到教廷、聯合國、世衛世乜都搞掂晒"}]}